::GoldenEye::

"Oh, well then.  I guess then I'll go now. It was nice talking to 
you.  I hope to see you around some time. Bye."  With that, she 
opened her wings and tookoff threw the trees.  She flew off about a 
mile or so away from where she had left the rat.  she perched on a 
tree branch and sighed.  She was no closer to solving her problem as 
she was earlier.  She sighed and looked at the ground.
